WEBVTT

00:10:58.950 --> 00:11:00.612
jambo moja,

00:11:00.636 --> 00:11:04.298
ubunifu mmoja unaweza ongeza namna,

00:11:04.322 --> 00:11:05.852
kubadili mchakato

00:11:05.876 --> 00:11:07.770
na hata kuokoa maisha.

00:11:08.599 --> 00:11:12.352
Nimekuwa nikifundisha maarifa ya uono
kwa miaka zaidi ya 15,

00:11:12.376 --> 00:11:15.592
na kwa mshangao wangu mkubwa
na ustaajabu --

00:11:15.616 --> 00:11:18.392
kwa mshangao na ustaajabu
usiokoma,

00:11:18.416 --> 00:11:21.944
Nimeona kwamba kuangalia kazi ya sanaa
na jicho la ukaribu

00:11:21.968 --> 00:11:25.380
kunaweza kutusaidia katika dunia yetu
ya maji yasiyopimwa,

00:11:25.404 --> 00:11:27.643
kama upo katika jeshi,

00:11:27.667 --> 00:11:30.616
mtoa msaada, tabibu au mama.